information regarding the leucovorin shortage, please see the Discussion. e See NCCN Guidelines for Management of Immunotherapy-Related Toxicities.

i If no prior tumor progression while on therapy with a checkpoint inhibitor. k Systemic therapy regimen dosing and schedules are based on extrapolations from
